data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features a desirable split bedroom plan, offering privacy and space for everyone. The cozy living room boasts a charming gas log fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings. The large kitchen is complete with ample counter space, plenty of cabinets, and a spacious dining area for entertaining guests. A big utility room with a convenient sink adds functionality and convenience to the home. Step outside onto the covered deck and enjoy the peaceful surroundings of the large corner lot. Additionally, this property includes a 2 car attached garage for added convenience.
